IANAStorageMediaType.name: IANAStorageMediaType
IANAStorageMediaType.description: The media type of a storage device: unknown(1) The media type is unknown, e.g., because the implementation failed to obtain the media type from the hypervisor. other(2) The media type is other than those defined in this conversion. hardDisk(3) The media type is hard disk. opticalDisk(4) The media type is optical disk. floppyDisk(5) The media type is floppy disk.
